261
00:32:42,799 --> 00:32:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] Spominjem taj period samaštva jer to onda računam neka mlada osoba,

262
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] dobro je da baš u tom periodu ipak radiš više na sebi.

263
00:32:49,519 --> 00:32:51,720
