284
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] možda ću fula prezime, ali bila je u podcastu

285
00:33:48,519 --> 00:33:50,039
[SPEAKER_00] Rastući s djecom, predivno je to rekla.

286
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] One stvari, kad ljudi tek hodaju,

287
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:57,259
[SPEAKER_00] ono dobro što voliš se čini kao planina

288
00:33:57,259 --> 00:33:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] i samo u to gledaš.

289
00:33:58,519 --> 00:34:01,160
[SPEAKER_00] A oneki problem i ono što bi mi je rekla danas red flag,

290
00:34:01,220 --> 00:34:02,240
[SPEAKER_00] to su neki kamenčići.

291
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] Fast forward, kasnije 10, 15, 20 godina u braku,

292
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:08,639
[SPEAKER_00] ta planina nestane, pretvori se u kamenčići,

293
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] ti to više ni ne vidiš, ni ne sjećaš se,

294
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] misli, to je neki sad, ono, ružan scenarij,

295
00:34:13,039 --> 00:34:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] ni ne sjećaš se što si to vidio,

296
00:34:14,519 --> 00:34:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] a taj kamenčić izraste u planinu

297
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] i postane kamen spotica.

298
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zato se treba, između ostalog,

299
00:34:20,719 --> 00:34:22,320
[SPEAKER_00] ipak fokusirati na te kamenčiće

300
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjeti mogu li oni,

301
00:34:24,519 --> 00:34:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] jesu li oni te neke nesavršenosti

302
00:34:26,420 --> 00:34:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] koje možeš prihvatiti

303
00:34:27,559 --> 00:34:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] u okviru toga da je ta osoba jednostavno nesavršen

304
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] kao što si i ti,

305
00:34:31,599 --> 00:34:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] ali je dostojanstveno ljubljeno djete Božje

306
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] i da to gledaš u njemu,

307
00:34:39,659 --> 00:34:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] ili je to nešto što će prerasti u planinu

308
00:34:43,659 --> 00:34:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] i nećeš moći preći preko toga.

309
00:34:44,940 --> 00:34:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ipak treba odvagnut neke stvari.

310
00:34:47,739 --> 00:34:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nije sve samo kemija, izgodanje, visok crni.

311
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ne daš mi da pređem na muža, još se držim ovdje.

312
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:57,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, oni ne želi previše biti eksponirati.

313
00:34:57,219 --> 00:34:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne

314
00:34:57,460 --> 00:34:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

315
00:34:58,300 --> 00:35:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ne ga konkretno, ne bi općenito na instituciju.

316
00:35:00,500 --> 00:35:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Instituciju supruga.

317
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,980
[SPEAKER_02] Koji su to kamenči?

318
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:05,400
[SPEAKER_02] Koji su to red flag-ovi?

319
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:08,079
[SPEAKER_02] Sad dođeti cura, ima 20 godina priča s tom.

320
00:35:08,079 --> 00:35:08,639
[SPEAKER_02] Šta je to?

321
00:35:08,639 --> 00:35:10,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ok, imaju karakterne savršenosti.

322
00:35:10,539 --> 00:35:11,500
[SPEAKER_02] Npr. neko je nagal.

323
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:13,320
[SPEAKER_02] Neko je impulzivan.

324
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:16,400
[SPEAKER_02] Neko je opet malo povučeniji, pa bi ti htjela da vam budge malo ovak.

325
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:19,559
[SPEAKER_02] Znači to su neke savršenosti koje ti kreposnim načinom života možeš ispraviti.

326
00:35:19,559 --> 00:35:22,059
