378
00:39:26,119 --> 00:39:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] traže takvu jednu figuru.

379
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] I ti, kao što sam spomenula na početku,

380
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:33,440
